{
  "stem": "14687.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 151,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "One-- one of your friends?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 152,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 153,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not anymore.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 153,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she was-- she was 16, 17.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 153,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was young.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 154,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, they used to put-- yeah, they put [NON-ENGLISH], they used to call it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 155,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They told me, the people there-- the French, that lady.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 155,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She said they put things, no, not to come that thing, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 155,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 156,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the food they use to put, but we didn't know nothing, you see?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 156,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just went there maybe we were malnoutritions.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 156,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had no food, that's why.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 157,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Myself, I haven't got very much, on-- very fine hair, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 158,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And rheumatism terrible, you know, from the--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 159,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ooh!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 159,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A lot-- my legs, my foot, and my arms, you know, from buckets.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 160,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, with no shoes-- nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 160,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were-- and we never saw the snow in Rhodos.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 160,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now there is snow everywhere.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 160,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But before, they didn't.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 160,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 161,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Recovery.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 161,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "People--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 162,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--it was Jewish-- the-- all the Jewish people there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 162,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, it was very nice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 162,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They treat us very nice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 162,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "After--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 163,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no, no working-- sitting, eating all day, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 163,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They gave us chocolate.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 163,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They gave us garlic.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 164,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No-- the Russians, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 164,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They throw away cigarettes to us, chocolates.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 165,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were so happy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 165,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then what we did is-- [NON-ENGLISH], you know, Rochelle, she was married to Flor's brother, Kapuluto.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 165,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So now-- she said now is the time we are going to go and-- and-- and pinch things.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 165,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we pinch all these pillow cases.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 165,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was all plumas, what do you call?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 165,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "All--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 166,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--feathers.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 166,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We used to-- and then from that material, we used to make shirts for us, you know, to change ourselves.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 166,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was very nice, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 167,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then we saw all the Germans running like the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
